OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FShowers
OL,6,Feasing this evening to leave late
OL,7,Fsunny spells. Cool to begin the night
OL,8,Funder clear skies, but temperatures
OL,9,Frebounding slightly as cloud builds,
OL,10,Fand rain moves in from the west,
OL,11,Fduring the early hours of Thursday.
OL,12,
OL,13,CThursday:FA wet and windy day as rain
OL,14,Fspreads across the region, turning
OL,15,Flocally heavy at times. Feeling muggy
OL,16,Funder widespread cloud cover. A little
OL,17,Fdrier by the evening with showers.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
