OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FLargely
OL,6,Fcloudy and breezy on Friday with
OL,7,Fpatchy rain. Some showers possible on
OL,8,FSaturday. Otherwise becoming drier and
OL,9,Fwarmer over the weekend with sunny
OL,10,Fspells. Winds easing.
